@startuml BK_Restaurant_Order_State_Machine
title BK Restaurant Management System\nOrder State Machine Diagram
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #EAF3DE
    BorderColor #3B6D11
    FontColor #173404
}
[*] --> OrderPlaced : Customer order received\n(Phone / WhatsApp)
OrderPlaced --> OrderConfirmed : Cashier confirms order
OrderPlaced --> Cancelled : Order cancelled
OrderConfirmed --> Preparing : Kitchen starts preparation
Preparing --> ReadyForPickup : Dine-in / Takeaway Order
Preparing --> ReadyForDelivery : Delivery Order
Preparing --> Cancelled : Order cancelled
ReadyForPickup --> PaymentCompleted : Payment received
ReadyForDelivery --> AssignedToRider : Rider assigned
AssignedToRider --> OutForDelivery : Rider picks up order
OutForDelivery --> Delivered : Delivery completed
OutForDelivery --> DeliveryFailed : Customer unavailable
DeliveryFailed --> OutForDelivery : Reattempt delivery
DeliveryFailed --> Cancelled : Delivery cancelled
Delivered --> PaymentCompleted : Payment verified
PaymentCompleted --> Completed : Order closed
Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]
state OrderPlaced
state OrderConfirmed
state Preparing
state ReadyForPickup
state ReadyForDelivery
state AssignedToRider
state OutForDelivery
state Delivered
state DeliveryFailed
state PaymentCompleted
state Completed
state Cancelled
note right of Preparing
Kitchen staff prepares food.
Inventory is updated based on
ordered menu items.
end note
note right of AssignedToRider
Delivery Service assigns
an available rider.
end note
note right of PaymentCompleted
Billing Service records
successful payment and
generates invoice.
end note
note right of Delivered
Order successfully delivered
to customer.
end note
@enduml
